OL,5, Social services raised concerns about a
OL,6, violent offender weeks before he was   
OL,7, deemed fit for bail and went on to     
OL,8, murder his girlfriend.                 
OL,10,FChristopher McGowan tortured Claire    
OL,11,FInglis before killing her at her flat  
OL,12,Fin Stirling on 28 November 2021.       
OL,14,FDocuments seen by the BBC show the case
OL,15,Fwas flagged to social workers in       
OL,16,FSeptember and they tried to visit the  
OL,17,Fproperty three days before the killing.
OL,19,FThe council said reports on McGowan    
OL,20,Fwere not requested by the courts.      
